text: KIOO is a classic rock formatted broadcast radio station licensed to Porterville, California, serving the Visalia/Tulare area. KIOO is owned and operated by Momentum Broadcasting LP. ==External links== *99.7 Classic Rock Online IOO Category:Classic rock radio stations in the United States Category:Mass media in Tulare County, California Category:Porterville, California Category:Radio stations established in 1990 Category:1990 establishments in California
